units.name: Lesser Demon Cat
units.description: A mad cat that sacrificed itself to a demon from the netherworld. Attacks with extreme force.

units.name: Greater Demon Cat
units.description: The mad cat managed to control the demon from the netherworld. Attacks with extreme force.

units.name: Greater Balrog Cat
units.description: His wanderings through the abyss have driven him mad with infernal ambitions. Tremendous damage to a single enemy.

units.name: Wonder MOMOCO
units.description: Cosmic policegirl hunting interdimensional criminals with lovely plasma beams of justice. Freezes Red/Black/Angels with Wave Attacks.

units.name: Cutie MOMOCO
units.description: The galaxy\'s most stylish detective, cleaning up cosmic crime with her cutting edge Cutie Beam. Area attacks freeze Red/Black/Angels.

units.name: Ice Cat
units.description: A cat was entranced by a girl hailing from the Land of Ice. It is frozen. Might stop Red enemies. (Area Attack)

units.name: Ice Queen Cat
units.description: Forgot to mention that the Cat is an eternal icicle. Don\'t think it complains much. Might stop Red enemies. (Area Attack)

units.name: Ice Crystal Cat
units.description: The Ice Queen\'s reign grows more secure and so does her Cat companion\'s crystal shell. Freezes Red enemies in place (Area Attack).

units.name: Cat Machine
units.description: Series 1 Weaponized Machine System (MS) developed by the government (Area Attack) Resistant to Red & Alien attacks.

units.name: Cat Machine Mk 2
units.description: A battle-tested revision MS that managed to escape from the research facility (Area Attack) Resistant to Red & Alien attacks.

units.name: Cat Machine Mk 3
units.description: The next generation of battle tech, MS:RX-Î© has slipped into the hands of the Cat Army! Resists Red/Alien attacks, immune to Waves.

units.name: Marauder Cat
units.description: Its cursed sword reduces the offensive power but might deliver critical hits. Known as the "Metal Killer".

units.name: Berserker Cat
units.description: The cursed sword has taken over and turned the Cat into the Cursed Knight. Known as the "Dark Metal Knight". (Area Atk)

units.name: Paladin Cat
units.description: This Cat\'s righteous heart finally conquered the cursed sword, turning it into a holy axe. Might critical attack. (Area Attack)

units.name: Baby Cat
units.description: A baby Cat that still can\'t do anything by itself. Luckily, daddy is there to help. Might knockback Floating & Aliens (Area Atk)

units.name: Baby Cats
units.description: Brought along its baby sister. Dad has his work cut out for him. Might knockback Floating & Aliens (Area Atk)

units.name: Cats in the Cradle
units.description: Even 7 kittens together can\'t do much... Luckily Dad\'s still keeping an eye out for bullies. Area wave attacks knockback Floating/Alien.

units.name: Nurse Cat
units.description: Her warm smile and healing aura take away the sting of her piercing syringe (Area attack) Might knockback/slow Black/Floating enemies.

units.name: Heartful Nurse Cat
units.description: A battlefield nurse saving lives with a syringe. Defensive power/area increased (Area attack) Might knockback/slow Black/Floating enemies.

units.name: Joyful Nurse Cat
units.description: A beloved medic & veteran of many Cat campaigns. Area attacks deliver vital medicine. Might knockback/slow Black/Floating enemies.

units.name: Cat Clan Heroes
units.description: A brave band of cats out to defeat the King of Evil. Long-Range Area strikes have chance of Critical. 100% chance to weaken Red, Black, and Floating.

units.name: Cat Guild Heroes
units.description: The Chosen One and 11 courageous adventurers. Long-Range Area strikes have chance of Critical. 100% chance to weaken Red, Black, and Floating.

units.name: Cat Quest Heroes
units.description: Our adventurers take their quest to the skies! Long-range Area strikes have chance of Critical. 100% Weaken vs Red, Black, Floating, Relics.

units.name: Lasvoss
units.description: Incarnation of evil summoned to eradicate the forces of Good. May strike a Savage Blow imbued with dark power. Survives once, stronger after taking damage.

units.name: Ultimate Lasvoss
units.description: His final form, revealed for the final confrontation with the heroes. Smites adventurers with Savage Blows. Survives once, stronger after taking damage.

units.name: Lasvoss Reborn
units.description: Will arise only on the eve of the world\'s destruction. Cloaked in darkness, his claws obliterate naive heroes, leaving no trace of their pitiful existence.

units.name: Summoner Satoru
units.description: To save the world, this boy made a pact with the Aku. Commands dark minions for a good cause... for now. Long-range Area attacks, 100% Slow vs Aku

units.name: Dark Summoner Satoru
units.description: Only a pure desire to save the world keeps Satoru from being corrupted by the magic of the Aku pact. Long-range Area attacks, 100% Slow vs Aku

units.name: Cat Tengu
units.description: Cat that endured all manner of difficult training in the mountains to become a yokai. Colossus Slayer, strong against Red/Angels, sometimes Knockback.

units.name: Grand Yokai Tengu
units.description: Mysterious Cat that awoke its deepest mental faculties with harsh training. Wields fire & wind. Colossus Slayer, strong against Red/Angels, sometimes Knockback.

units.name: Legeluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about that pandimensional crystal...

units.name: Legelan Pasalan
units.description: Gaze upon its might and tremble! There\'s no doubt that this one is immune to Wave damage (Omni-Strike)

units.name: Nekoluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... Maybe if you evolve him...

units.name: Unknown Cat
units.description: God, I don\'t know if this is a Cat anymore. Seriously, I give up. Knockbacks enemies. (Area Atk.)

units.name: Ultralan Pasalan
units.description: Tired of scaring children, Luga decided to reinvent himself as that famous masked hero. Freezes and knocks back non-Metal enemies (Area Atk.)

units.name: Asiluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about those legs...

units.name: Asilan Pasalan
units.description: Unbelievable, just unbelievable. Seems like this one slows all enemies in range.

units.name: Assassinlan Pasalan
units.description: Is it a Cat? Or an overly melodramatic comic-book assassin of some kind? Slows enemies with Area Attacks.

units.name: Kubiluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about that neck...

units.name: Kubilan Pasalan
units.description: You can\'t be serious. Really?! Seems like this one knocks back enemies from afar.

units.name: E. Kubilan Pasalan
units.description: A mighty sumo wrestler who sharpened his expert skills fighting on the streets. Wave attacks with 100% Critical chance!

units.name: Tecoluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about those arms...

units.name: Tesalan Pasalan
units.description: Are you kidding me?! Seems like this one does massive damage (sometimes critical) to just one enemy.

units.name: Lufalan Pasalan
units.description: It seems like this one is a straw-hatted pirate of some kind. But we really can\'t be sure. Massive damage vs. one enemy. (Might Crit.)

units.name: Balaluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about that belly...

units.name: Balalan Pasalan
units.description: No. Way. This can\'t be right... Seems like this one freezes all enemies in range.

units.name: Piccolan Pasalan
units.description: A totally unknown extraterrestrial lifeform of unimaginable power... or maybe just a weird Cat? Freezes and weakens all enemies in area atk range.

units.name: Togeluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about those... spikes???

units.name: Togelan Pasalan
units.description: No. Way. This can\'t be right... Survives one lethal strike, get stronger the more damage he takes. (Area Attack)

units.name: Shishilan Pasalan
units.description: Ancient god who bridges the worlds of the living and the dead. Survives once, grows stronger as he takes more damage. (Area Attack)

units.name: Nobiluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about that cool \'stache...

units.name: Nobilan Pasalan
units.description: I can\'t stand it anymore... Seems like this one is immune to Wave attacks. (Long Range Area Attack)

units.name: Mystican Pasalan
units.description: Monster? Magician? ...Or just a Cat? No one can explain how its powers work. Immune to Wave attacks (Long-Range Area)

units.name: Papaluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about that toothless smile...

units.name: Papalan Pasalan
units.description: Great googly moogly! Seems like this mysterious old-timer has Area attacks that 100% Curse non-Metal.

units.name: Sukelan Kakulan
units.description: An average pensioner, or a mysterious force of eldritch destruction? Best not to think about it. 100% Curse vs non-Metal, Immune to Surge Attacks.

units.name: Furiluga
units.description: Not sure if this is a Cat... There\'s just something about those burning locks of hair...

units.name: Furilan Pasalan
units.description: Can the world take any more of these?! Seems like this one has Area attacks that 100% Pierce and Barrier Break

units.name: Musashi Miyamoto
units.description: A wandering swordsman who has travelled to the realm of carnage to master the Nichirin Blade. Tough vs. / Insane Damage vs. Black.

units.name: Wargod Miyamoto
units.description: The blood on his hands transformed the Nichirin into a cursed Getsurin sword. You have no chance. Tough vs. / Insane Damage vs. Black.

units.name: Sanada Yukimura
units.description: A famous warrior that was transformed by the Legendary Cat Armor into a bird-type General. Deals massive damage to Black enemies.

units.name: Wargod Yukimura
units.description: Activated the armor\'s hidden function "Jet Boosters". No stopping it now! Deals massive damage to Black enemies.

units.name: Immortal Yukimura
units.description: Crimson wings carry this wargod through the front lines, tearing them apart without mercy! Deals massive damage to black enemies.

units.name: Maeda Keiji
units.description: A warrior that was transformed by the Legendary Cat Armour into a Tiger-type General. (Area Attack) Resistant to Black, more damage when hurt.

units.name: Wargod Keiji
units.description: The Legendary Cat Armor evolved and sprouted a Cherry Tree from his head (Area Attack) Resistant to Black, more damage when hurt.

units.name: Immortal Keiji
units.description: As the cherries blossom, so does Keiji\'s battle fury. Resistant to Black, immune to Wave attacks. Area attacks grow stronger as he takes damage.

units.name: Oda Nobunaga
units.description: The manifestation of the Grudge of Nobunaga from the lives of many (and one Cat) (Area Attack) Stops the movements of Black enemies.

units.name: Wargod Nobunaga
units.description: The Cat\'s spirit goes into overdrive. The grudge grows even stronger. (Area Attack) Stops the movement of Black enemies.

units.name: Immortal Nobunaga
units.description: Leads an army of vengeful spirits to fulfill his dream of unifying the heavens and the netherworld. 100% chance to Freeze Black enemies. (Area)

units.name: Date Masamune
units.description: The curse of the Legendary Cat Shield has made him a killing machine. (Area attack) Might knock back Black and Red enemies.

units.name: Wargod Masamune
units.description: Cat Shield\'s Hell Mode - activate! Infernal (Area) attacks slice through his foes! Might knock back Black and Red enemies.

units.name: Immortal Masamune
units.description: Infernal hatred has fully infused the shield. Karmic blades sweep through all enemies! Area attacks. Knockback Black and Red enemies.

units.name: Takeda Shingen
units.description: A master tactician of overwhelming power who is cursed by the Legendary Cat Sword. Area attacks only damage Black/Aliens.

units.name: Wargod Shingen
units.description: Cat Sword\'s Tactics Mode - activate! Even greater destructive power! Area attacks only damage Black/Aliens.

units.name: Immortal Shingen
units.description: The Cat Sword\'s path of destruction is unstoppable. There is no mercy to be given. Area attacks only damage Black/Aliens.

units.name: Uesugi Kenshin
units.description: Transformed into a dragon through the cursed magic of the Nyanko Engine. (Area attack) Strong + 100% knockback against Black.

units.name: Wargod Kenshin
units.description: Deciding to fully fuse with the Nyanko Engine, the great general gave in to darkness (Area att.) Strong + 100% knockback against Black.

units.name: Immortal Kenshin
units.description: Totally consumed by corruption. The only emotion remaining is the will to destruction. (Area Attacks) Strong vs + 100% knockback against Black.

units.name: Imagawa Yoshimoto
units.description: His impeccable virtue allows him to wield the cursed Cat Fan. Strong against Black, 100% chance to weaken (Long-range)

units.name: Wargod Yoshimoto
units.description: Possessed by an all-knowing fox spirit, he strikes with golden arrows. Strong vs Black, 100% chance to weaken (Long-range)

units.name: Immortal Yoshimoto
units.description: Stained crimson with the blood of his rivals, the Cat Fan burns with an unearthly fire for even greater damage and weakening against Black enemies.

units.name: Narita Kaihime
units.description: This stunning warrior has been blessed with an invincible blade and a resolute body. Slows Black/Zombies, might strike Savage blows.

units.name: Wargod Kaihime
units.description: Incomparable beauty who mercilessly destroys foes while maintaining perfect composure in battle. Slows Black/Zombies, might strike Savage blows.

units.name: Immortal Kaihime
units.description: This dignified heroine has withstood the corruption of the cursed weapons and seeks only to bring peace. 100% Slow vs Black/Zombies, chance of Savage blows.

units.name: Shiro Amakusa
units.description: Clockwork creation imbued with a young zealot\'s soul. Driven to bloody battle for his righteous cause. Massive Area damage vs Aku and Black enemies.

units.name: Wargod Amakusa
units.description: His endless crusade has stained his own spirit, turning him into a vengeful wraith of slaughter. Massive Area damage vs Aku and Black enemies.

units.name: Immortal Amakusa
units.description: Embodiment of grudges and rage on the battlefield. Houses vengeful hellfire that will bring the world to ruin. Massive Area damage vs Aku and Black enemies.

units.name: Hattori Hanzo
units.description: Ninja transformed into a panther by a cursed iaito. One swift strike, and the mission is complete. Colossus Slayer, Massive damage to Black/Floating, 100% Freeze.

units.name: Wargod Hanzo
units.description: Peerless assassin who cuts down targets with godspeed, unleashing the power of his cursed blade. Colossus Slayer, massive damage to Black/Floating, 100% Freeze.

units.name: Headmistress Jeanne
units.description: Chairwoman of the Cyber Academy, respected by all. Summons ethereal spears to punish bad students. Insane damage to Red/Floating. (Long-Range/Area)

units.name: Headmistress Jeanne Ï
units.description: Her educational philosophy has become more... unforgiving lately. But who\'s going to complain? Insane damage to Red/Floating. (Long-Range/Area)

units.name: Windy
units.description: A galaxy girl who manipulates wind. Her vacuum cannon cleans enemies from a distance. Massive damage to Floating enemies (Area Attack).

units.name: Windy type Î±
units.description: This strange girl can hear the wind whispering. The wind tells her that it is in pain... Massive damage to Floating enemies (Area Attack).

units.name: Divine Windy
units.description: Has a bad habit of impulse buying the latest mechas. Neo-Vacuum Cannon blasts from long-distance. Massive damage to Floating enemies (Area Attack).

units.name: Thundia
units.description: A galaxy girl who can manipulate electricity. Brings down bolts from a distance. Massive damage to Red enemies (Area Attack).

units.name: Thundia type Î²
units.description: Always worries about her chronic neck pain. Likes watching cartoons in her spare time. Massive damage to Red enemies (Area Attack).

units.name: Divine Thundia
units.description: When you have a goddess\' body, it\'s tough to find clothes that fit. Long distance Area Attacks deliver massive damage to Red enemies.

units.name: Kuu
units.description: Zealous user of strange witchcraft to control her staff for great damage from a distance. Strong against Black/Red enemies. (Area Attack)

units.name: Kuu, type Î³
units.description: Zealous user of strange witchcraft. Not good with men, ends with verbal abuse. Strong against Black/Red enemies. (Area Attack)

units.name: Divine Kuu
units.description: Treat her like a weakling and you\'ll know true pain. Your apologies will only make the staff smash down harder. Strong against Red/Black (Area Attack).

units.name: Kai
units.description: Airheaded girl riding her machine pig "Tonton". Fires powerful point blank beams (Area Attack). Reduced damage from Floating, survives once.

units.name: Kai type Î¼
units.description: Ends up liking anyone who is nice to her. Her love hurdle is mere 3cm (Area Attack). Reduced damage from Floating, survives once.

units.name: Divine Kai
units.description: If any cute guy is your type, is that really a type? Always travels via her trusty Boarborg (Area Atk) Reduced damage from Flying, Survives Once.

units.name: Coppermine
units.description: Magical beauty powered by her staff Releases beams of light (Area Attack) Might freeze floating enemies.

units.name: Coppermine, type Îº
units.description: Doesn\'t smile that often. (Area Attack) In front of cats, however.. different story. Might stop floating enemies.

units.name: Divine Coppermine
units.description: What can you do for her that her favorite cat doesn\'t already? Come back in 100 years, kid. Might stop Floating(Area Attack)

units.name: Kalisa
units.description: Almost obliterated her school on the first day of class with her sword\'s dark magic. Massive damage against Angels. (Area Attack)

units.name: Kalisa, type Ï
units.description: Banished her principal to the netherworld at the graduation ceremony. Things never change. Massive damage against Angels. (Area Attack)

units.name: Divine Kalisa
units.description: All of the nice boys who confess their love to her soon find themselves "graduated" to the next world. Massive damage against Angels (Area Attack)

units.name: Twinstars
units.description: The two purehearted sisters, Cici and Koma. Divine breath controls their mighty mecha claws. Massive area damage to Aliens/Black.

units.name: Twinstars, type Î¦
units.description: The mechanical catpaws "AH" and "UN" sweetly sweep away any threat to these cutie-pie demigods. Massive area damage to Aliens/Black.

units.name: Divine Twinstars
units.description: Undisputed masters of the coordinated assault. They skipped detention today to join the battle! Massive area damage to Aliens/Black.

units.name: Myrcia
units.description: Money couldn\'t buy happiness, but it bought a small arsenal that very much brings a smile to her face. Wave Attacks, might dodge Traitless enemy attacks.

units.name: Myrcia, type Î¾
units.description: RoboButler is endlessly apologizing for Myr\'s rich-girl faux pas (and the trail of destruction left in her wake). Wave Attacks, might dodge Traitless enemy attacks.

units.name: Divine Myrcia
units.description: Bourgeois space princess living a high-class life, but can\'t resist cravings for cheap cheeseburgers. Wave attacks, might dodge Traitless enemy attacks.

units.name: Lilin
units.description: This mad researcher experimented on her own classmates to synthesize the vile Mateki elixir. Strong vs Angels & Aku, with Piercing attacks.

units.name: Lilin Ï
units.description: Made a pact with the evil Aku to attain the ultimate Mateki formula and enslave the entire Academy. Strong vs Angels & Aku, with 100% Piercing attacks.

units.name: Divine Lilin Ï
units.description: A madwoman who creates elixirs to enslave demons. Gazes on calamity and chaos with a bewitching grin. Strong vs Angels & Aku, with 100% Piercing attacks.

units.name: Huntress Terun
units.description: Invited along on a hunt, her life was forever changed. Hounds her prey with blasts from her Lightning Bow. Colossus Slayer, Area Attacks Slow Red/Aliens

units.name: Huntress Terun Î¶
units.description: Supernaturally calm and clever, she strikes without fail at the weakest point of her gargantuan quarry. Colossus Slayer, Area Attacks Slow Red/Aliens

units.name: High Lord Babel
units.description: The original dragon who became one with the heavenly castle that controls the mortal realms. Insanely tough vs. Red/Floating (Area Attack).

units.name: Babel the Darkflame
units.description: His dragonic nature has been slowly corrupting the heavenly castle over many millennia... Insanely tough vs. Red/Floating (Area Attack)

units.name: Sodom
units.description: An awakened Ancient Cat Dragon. Leaves destruction in its wake (Area Attack) Might knockback/resistant to Floating.

units.name: Earth King Sodom
units.description: An awakened Ancient Cat Dragon Weapon. Shifted to his final Dragon form (Area Attack) Might knockback/resistant to Floating.

units.name: God-Emperor Sodom
units.description: Sodom unlocked his FINAL final Dragon form, rending the very earth asunder with his power! 100% area knockback/resistant vs Floating.

units.name: Baby Gao
units.description: Might be a crybaby but he\'s still young! He just doesn\'t realize the power within himself. Strong against every enemy with a trait. (Area Atk)

units.name: Mighty Lord Gao
units.description: Only appears to those who seek true power. Strong against every enemy with a trait, immune to Wave attacks. Might critical (Area Atk).
